snippet.title: Meteorfall: Krumit's Tale
snippet.description: Meteorfall: Krumit's Tale is the second game in the 'Meteorfall' universe.  This new deckbuilding roguelike is coming to Steam Early Access in 2019.  Learn more: http://www.krumits-tale.com
